Chrome Glass Remastered - acknowledgement
=========================================

Chrome Glass Remastered is an unofficial, derivative remaster of:

    "Chrome Glass" by yoyos
    Published on DeviantArt, 23 April 2006
    https://www.deviantart.com/yoyos/art/Chrome-Glass-32252748

The cursor frames in src/orig/ are the original 2006 bitmaps; the frames in
src/ai/ and everything built from them (dist/, release archives, previews)
are derived from those bitmaps: AI upscaling, colour restoration and
vector-traced edges applied on top of the original artist's work. The Pin
and Person cursors are new drawings made for this set in the original's
style. The 32 px images inside the shipped cursors are the original frames,
byte for byte.

The "Chrome Glass" name and the original artwork remain the creative work
and property of their author; "HD" marks this as an unofficial remaster.
It is published as a tribute, in the belief that a free,
attribution-preserving revival of a 20-year-old classic is in its spirit.
If you are the author and want anything changed or removed, open an issue
and it will be done.

If you build on this project, keep this acknowledgement. Before any use
beyond this repository (forks aside), consider contacting the original
author on DeviantArt.

The MIT license in LICENSE covers the code only (build pipeline, tracing,
rendering and packaging tools), not the cursor artwork.
